      "headline": "Healthcare and NHS access",
      "shortSummary": "Restore Britain says the NHS should be restored as a national health service serving British people first. Its healthcare pledges include free parking for NHS staff, patients and visitors, removing medical school caps, and prioritising British-trained doctors.",
